    "body": "I just checked and this is still reproducible in our CI with latest solc: [1249604](https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/ethereum/solidity/28161/workflows/1537f3cb-2e7b-4461-9792-03474dcbe9d6/jobs/1249604)\r\n\r\n```\r\n254 passing (17s)\r\n  20 pending\r\n  2 failing\r\n\r\n  1) CompatibilityFallbackHandler\r\n       isValidSignature(bytes,bytes)\r\n         should revert if called directly:\r\n     AssertionError: Expected transaction to be reverted with function call to a non-contract account, but other exception was thrown: Error: Transaction reverted without a reason string\r\n  \r\n\r\n  2) CompatibilityFallbackHandler\r\n       isValidSignature(bytes32,bytes)\r\n         should revert if called directly:\r\n     AssertionError: Expected transaction to be reverted with function call to a non-contract account, but other exception was thrown: Error: Transaction reverted without a reason string\r\n```\r\n\r\nSame locally, on 0.8.10 and without all the overrides we do in CI:\r\n```bash\r\ngit clone https://github.com/safe-global/safe-contracts.git\r\ncd safe-contracts/\r\nexport SOLIDITY_VERSION=0.8.10\r\nnpm install\r\nnpm install hardhat@latest\r\nnpm test test/handlers/CompatibilityFallbackHandler.spec.ts\r\n```",
